h1. Installation

h2. Overview

This section describes how to install the @LdapService@ plugin.

h2. Install Plugin

The @LdapService@ plugin is installed like any other plugin. It can be added to @BuildConfig.groovy@ like so:

{code}
plugins {
    compile 'com.socialidm.ldap-service:0.1.0'
}
{code}

Or you can install it from the command line from the root directory of your project:

{code}
grails install-plugin ldap-service
{code}